### Ninja IDE Git Plugin

Plugin for Ninja IDE that enables git calls from the IDE itself via a integrated GUI. To see it in action, check [this video](http://youtu.be/U4xjL0bWXUA) out

It use a window for managing git calls. The way the plugin works is needed to have open and be editing (in the current focus) any file of the project that you want to use with git.

### Features

- add git support for project
- stage,unstage,commit,uncommit files
- create,change,merge,delete branches
- highlight changes in files(diff)
